Open baseline (this repository; npm packages "patina-cli" and "patina-humanizer")
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The pattern packs, the deterministic stylometry/lexicon analyzer, the scorer,
and the bundled backends — including the `patina-hosted` adapter and its
versioned request/response schema — are part of the open baseline and are
covered by the MIT License.

Hosted track (NOT included here)
--------------------------------
The reinforced Korean detection assets (corpus, lexicon, patterns), the
reinforced LLM/prompt pipeline, and the hosted server are maintained in a
separate, private project. They are reached only over the versioned hosted
schema via an explicit `--backend patina-hosted`, and are never published in
this repository or its npm packages.

